1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:21,600
 Evo nastavljamo. Natano kad palite automobil pa on neće. Pa kažemo ono,prisauga. Pa da mi ne bismo prisaugali, neće opet toliko dugo. Ja nemam sata pa sam uzio od ovoga gospodina. Prema tome, mogu ima reći ima jako težak sat. Mogu ja bi ti vremetincu završiti.

2
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:40,600
 Kako da kažu, svakao slično za stvarnim osobama je namjerno. E, slučajno, dobro. Ovi snimate li znaće što je za izbrisat, što je interno, što je eksterno, li tako? To je tako? Ma ja. Oni su pametni.

3
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:51,600
 To je baš zanimljivo jer jedna je situacija kad smo mi ovdje jer mi smo zajednica. A drugo je kad čovjek neki samo kući to gleda, niti on zna vaša lica, ne zna ozračije, ne zna

4
00:00:51,600 --> 00:01:00,600
 na atmosferu, ne zna što sam ja dogovarao s Matijom i tako dalje. Jedan put on to drugačije shvate.

5
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:09,600
 Evo ga. Ali imam i divne ljude. Evo, tu ću ja staviti kao čisto da ja imam sad. To treba se danas pohvaliti.

6
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:22,600
 Ovako, meni je malo Matija govorio da pokušam nešto reći o hrabrosti, o važnosti, danas govoriti čak u našem društvenom životu.

7
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:34,600
 Meni uvi najdraže je govoriti da se razumijemo. Mene kad sam ja pisao svoju knjigu, prvu nisam šutio, drugo šutnja izdaja, uvijek su me pitali: što ti to radiš?

8
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:41,600
 Velja zato što mi se ne da. Ali živa istina je to. Meni se to stvarno ne da.

9
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:55,600
 Ali kad ja vidim da je sve se sakrilo u svoj strah, pobjeglo u svoj strah, onda se moram baviti i stvarima o kojima se ne volim baviti.

10
00:01:55,600 --> 00:02:10,600
 I ponekad možda čak mislim da gubim vrijeme, ali dok se ne nađe netko drugi, eto ja ću to pomalo, a pomalo se rađaju i oni drugi.

11
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:32,600
 Nameće se kultura, vidite, mi stalno živimo, ja bi vam mogao ovaj crtati, samo ja sam jako loš umjetnik, crtati bi vam mogao te paradokse ili proturiječija, bolje rečeno hrvatski, proturiječija koja vladaju općenito u svijetu i u nama.

12
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:51,980
 Vidite, stalno nam se govori o takozvanom imate pravo reći što hoćete, možete kao zapjevati što hoćete, premda je to upitno, znamo da ima pjesama koje se već malo manje pjevaju, a druge se malo više pjevaju i tako dalje.

13
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:56,480
 Pa možete kao iznet svoje mišljenje ima pravo na slobodu govora.

14
00:02:57,180 --> 00:03:03,500
 A nikada više nije bilo nametanja kulture šutnje.

15
00:03:03,500 --> 00:03:07,820
 U kojem smislu? Što to znači kultura šutnje?

16
00:03:07,820 --> 00:03:13,760
 Kultura šutnje nije da ti ne možeš izići ovdje sada ispred ove crkve i vikati,

17
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:17,340
 Jahve je moj bog i ja volim lucu.

18
00:03:19,340 --> 00:03:30,640
 Ne. Kultura je šutnje kad ti počimaš snositi konsekvence kada budeš kažnjen zbog toga što govoriš,

19
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:42,460
 jer se ne uklapaš u mainstream, ne uklapaš se u ono što želi čuti ovaj svijet koji je navio svoj ton samo na jednu frekvenciju.

20
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:49,820
 Ali kaže Božja riječ, kaže ako vi zašutite, proroci Boži, kamenje će progovoriti.

21
00:03:49,820 --> 00:03:54,000
 A stalno se, koga se najviše šutkuje crkva?

22
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:58,880
 Nikog se danas više ne želi ušutiti nego svećenike.

23
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:06,780
 Ne zato ni što su lijepi, ni što su ružni, ni što su ćelavi, ni što im je ime ovakvo,

24
00:04:06,780 --> 00:04:12,880
 nego samo iz jednog bitnog razloga, ne želi se čuti glas Isusa Krista.

25
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:23,760
 Dakle, mi ćemo na svim mogućim platformama, agendama vidjeti što se crkvaja, što svećenici govore, što ovi.

26
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:28,080
 Dakle, stalno se želi ušutkati Boži glas.

27
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:33,260
 E zato kaže Isus, ako vi zašutite, kamenje će progovoriti.

28
00:04:33,260 --> 00:04:34,980
 Ja se u to uvjeren.

29
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:40,680
 Zato govor, ja tu ohrabrijem koliko je moguće svećenike.

30
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:43,080
 Mi tu nemamo izbora.

31
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:49,940
 Pitanje govora nije moga hira ili moje odluke, sad sam ja negdje iz maloga prsta Isisa u odluku

32
00:04:49,940 --> 00:04:51,720
 i sad ću ja govor, ne, ne, ne.

33
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:57,020
 To je osnovno zaduženje poslanika Božijega.

34
00:04:57,020 --> 00:05:02,320
 Apostola, proroka, službenika Božijega.

35
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:06,220
 Govori, jer kaže pismo, bilo to zgodno ili ne zgodno.

36
00:05:06,220 --> 00:05:13,300
 Dakle, nije pitanje svećenika želi li ili ne želi govoriti.

37
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:20,280
 Nego je temeljno, ako ne govoriš, izdaješ svoje poslanje.

38
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:22,700
 Mi nemamo drugih alata.

39
00:05:22,700 --> 00:05:31,780
 Mi nemamo oružija, osim milosti Božije i sakramenata i govora Isusova, mi nemamo drugih alata i oružija.

40
00:05:31,780 --> 00:05:35,320
 Mi nemamo vojsku, Isus nije htio vojsku.

41
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:39,520
 Dakle, nameće se jedna kultura šutnje.

42
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:46,100
 I onda mi, dominantno kršćani, smo kao ušutkana, mi to kažemo često, ušutkana većina.

43
00:05:46,100 --> 00:05:49,060
 Dok je manjina jako glasna.

44
00:05:49,060 --> 00:05:52,040
 Oni kriče po ulicama, ne kriče oni.

45
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:54,240
 Zlo u njima viče.

46
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:58,720
 To je nešto Isus rekao, umukni, ušuti.

47
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:01,680
 Znam ja, tko si ti, kaže, zlo, svetac Boži.

48
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:10,480
 Pa bubnjaju, pa viču, pa jadnici sami sebe, ja bih rekao, javno prostituiraju.

49
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:16,100
 Vidite, kako je ta mala manjina u svijetu postala glasna?

50
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:22,120
 Vikom, galamom, hukom i bukom.

51
00:06:22,900 --> 00:06:26,940
 A u većinu kršćansku se želi ušutkati.

52
00:06:26,940 --> 00:06:29,920
 A mi na to nemamo pravo.

53
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:34,740
 Dakle, mi ne možemo doći u taj konfor da kažemo, ja neću govoriti.

54
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:39,720
 To je pitanje nasledovanja ili izdaje.

55
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:48,940
 Strah je metoda s kojom se zapravo provodi proces ušutkivanja

56
00:06:48,940 --> 00:06:52,820
 i provođenja programa koji nisu Božiji.

57
00:06:52,900 --> 00:06:59,020
 Ja ću namjeno rabiti reč koji nisu Boži, ne želeći previše davati propagandu

58
00:06:59,020 --> 00:07:01,860
 onima koji vode taj program pod drugim imenom.

59
00:07:01,860 --> 00:07:04,340
 Strah.

60
00:07:06,020 --> 00:07:11,000
 Rekao je Isus uzdrmati, udariti pastira, ovce će se razbjeći.

61
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:19,160
 Zato kad mi ovako, vidite koliko budu ljudi naivni, pazite, ko naime objavi se nešto o nekom svećeniku

62
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:25,080
 i onda kao dobri katolici, dobri katolici tamo komentiraju.

63
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:31,360
 A jadniče moj, ti ne znaš ako je udarem pastir da si ti udarem.

64
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:37,500
 Ako neko tamo tvoga nadbiskupa izruguje, tebe bolan izruguje.

65
00:07:37,500 --> 00:07:40,020
 Tebe izruguje.

66
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:48,440
 Ne moj biti truba onih čiji si postao dionik bez da to misliš da je tako.

67
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:53,820
 Danas imamo jedan paralelni svijet.

68
00:07:53,820 --> 00:08:05,260
 Osoba koje je to Bože, spašavajući crkvu, došli su do noga najbolje kamena dole i oni ga vade da se sve sruši.

69
00:08:05,260 --> 00:08:07,460
 A sve u ime spasenja crkve.

70
00:08:07,460 --> 00:08:12,020
 Ja imam predložbu modela određenih katolika.

71
00:08:12,020 --> 00:08:16,540
 Oni će zasa bređati, su veliki katolici, pravovjerni, nema to.

72
00:08:16,540 --> 00:08:21,540
 Oni već pomalo počinju, već su oni popravili.

73
00:08:21,540 --> 00:08:24,800
 Svećenike popravili su biskupe, papu su već popravili.

74
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,720
 E sad još malo Isusa treba popraviti.

75
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:30,260
 Oni su počeli Isusa popravljati.

76
00:08:30,260 --> 00:08:35,220
 E to je ta oholost.

77
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:37,320
 Oholost.

78
00:08:37,460 --> 00:08:40,380
 Tako je se strah se razvija.

79
00:08:40,380 --> 00:08:44,440
 Vidite i Perikle i Tukidid, filozof i veliki grčki kaže

80
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:48,800
 Pobjeda nad strahom početak je kreposti.

81
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:54,240
 Zato se nama u vremenu koje je iza nas,

82
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:59,680
 znate na koje vrijeme mislim, nije dostojno da mu spomenem ime,

83
00:09:00,940 --> 00:09:07,080
 gdje se zapravo preko straha ovladavalo našim životima.

84
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:12,380
 Gdje se nametne strah, nema prostora za kreposti.

85
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:15,920
 Kreposti su darovi Božiji.

86
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:23,240
 Dakle, ako živimo u strahu, oni znaju odvojeni smo od milosti, odvojeni smo od kreposti.

87
00:09:23,500 --> 00:09:25,800
 Nesposobni smo primjeti gospodina.

88
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:32,120
 Tajna, kaže, slobode je u hrabrosti, kaže Tukidid.

89
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:38,500
 I dodaje još on zajedno sa Periklom, tajna sreće je sloboda.

90
00:09:38,500 --> 00:09:42,480
 Sloboda nije dar ovog svijeta.

91
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:48,740
 Imamo ljude koji su plasnici mnogih nekretnina,

92
00:09:48,740 --> 00:09:51,680
 hodaju gdje hoće, putuju gdje hoće,

93
00:09:51,680 --> 00:09:54,920
 druže se s kim hoće, ali su zarobljeni.

94
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:56,320
 U zatvoru su.

95
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:59,580
 A imamo osoba, ja sam ih susrao i obilazio,

96
00:09:59,580 --> 00:10:02,420
 koji su u tamnici, u zatvoru, a na slobodi.

97
00:10:02,420 --> 00:10:07,440
 Dakle, sloboda nije pitanje vanjskog okruženja,

98
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:14,580
 nego nutarnjeg izbora i odluke da mi živimo slobodu,

99
00:10:14,580 --> 00:10:17,600
 koju nama ne daje nikakav sustav.

100
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:20,940
 Sloboda je Božiji dar.

101
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:25,880
 Vidite, na što se najviše udarilo u vremenu tog zla?

102
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:31,460
 Na slobodu i na savjest.

103
00:10:31,460 --> 00:10:35,520
 Na Božije instrumente u čovjeku.

104
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:38,480
 Dakle, na slobodu i na savjest se udarilo.

105
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:42,920
 I do zadnjeg se konca, konca gonilo,

106
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:48,240
 gdje su, nažalosti, neki teolozi se podmišlju činjenja dobra,

107
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:53,240
 čin ljubavi, svjetimo se tih priča,

108
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:58,560
 poče li savjest relativizirati.

109
00:10:58,560 --> 00:11:01,120
 Dakle, staviti dano nije, pa tako.

110
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:04,140
 Može i ovako, može i onako.

111
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:07,640
 Vidite, kad u nama uništite savjest,

112
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:10,140
 čovjek ne postoji.

113
00:11:10,140 --> 00:11:13,500
 Ne postoji.

114
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:14,820
 Može ti hodati.

115
00:11:14,820 --> 00:11:17,840
 Ti je lese tvoje, ali ti ne postojiš.

116
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:22,440
 Kad ti uzmu slobodu, ti ne postojiš.

117
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:26,480
 Što nam je, osim života,

118
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:29,200
 najveće što nam je Bog dao?

119
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,140
 To je ta slobodna volja, sloboda.

120
00:11:31,140 --> 00:11:35,660
 Čak ni Bog nije htio intervenirati

121
00:11:35,660 --> 00:11:37,140
 u ljudsku slobodu.

122
00:11:37,140 --> 00:11:37,820
 Ni Bog.

123
00:11:37,820 --> 00:11:40,820
 Pa stožer, bez problema.

124
00:11:40,820 --> 00:11:45,300
 Zamislite to.

125
00:11:45,300 --> 00:11:47,540
 Ni Bog.

126
00:11:47,540 --> 00:11:49,600
 Mi nekad čak i pregovaramo,

127
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,080
 pa Bože, što nas nisi stvorio,

128
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:54,620
 pa nam rekao ovo, ovako, ovako,

129
00:11:54,620 --> 00:11:56,280
 ne da mi sad možemo zalutati.

130
00:11:56,280 --> 00:11:56,860
 Ne, ne, ne, ne.

131
00:11:56,860 --> 00:12:00,500
 On hoće nas slobodne, ne kao robove.

132
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:02,460
 Svijet nas zarobljava,

133
00:12:02,460 --> 00:12:03,940
 a Bog nas oslobađa.

134
00:12:03,940 --> 00:12:05,860
 A opet dolazim u proturiječje.

135
00:12:05,860 --> 00:12:07,480
 Šta vi čujete često?

136
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:09,160
 Pa neću slijediti Boga,

137
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:10,440
 uzima mi slobodu,

138
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:12,200
 ograničava moje izbore,

139
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:14,880
 branim i ovo, branim i ono.

140
00:12:14,880 --> 00:12:16,200
 Veće vi to.

141
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:19,880
 Kako džavao unosi terminologiju

142
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:21,960
 u ono što nije istina.

143
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:26,240
 Dakle, jedini Bog nam dao slobodu.

144
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:29,740
 Jedini Bog nas ničim ne prisiljava,

145
00:12:29,740 --> 00:12:31,660
 ničim ne uvjetuje,

146
00:12:31,660 --> 00:12:33,320
 ničim ne nameće,

147
00:12:33,380 --> 00:12:34,280
 nego tko hoće,

148
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:35,400
 neka pođe za mnom,

149
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:37,200
 tko hoće, neka mi služi,

150
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:39,060
 tko hoće, neka uzme križma,

151
00:12:39,060 --> 00:12:40,840
 nikad ne piše moraš.

152
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:43,860
 Nikakva uvjeta.

153
00:12:43,860 --> 00:12:47,620
 A vidite, svijet nas svime uvjetuje

154
00:12:47,620 --> 00:12:50,600
 i kažu nam da Bog uzima nešto.

155
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:51,660
 Ne, Bog samo daje.

156
00:12:53,260 --> 00:12:58,940
 Bog samo daje, daje, daje, daje i daje.

157
00:12:59,020 --> 00:13:04,660
 zato je prava pravda je savjest.

158
00:13:04,660 --> 00:13:07,020
 To je pravda.

159
00:13:08,380 --> 00:13:13,680
 Znam ja da savjest može biti i osjetljiva,

160
00:13:13,680 --> 00:13:17,560
 skrupulozna, može biti i otupjela, okorjela,

161
00:13:17,560 --> 00:13:19,140
 može biti iskrivljena,

162
00:13:19,860 --> 00:13:21,140
 ali ljudi, dragi,

163
00:13:21,140 --> 00:13:22,460
 ajmo jedan put,

164
00:13:22,460 --> 00:13:25,200
 ajmo jedan put riješiti

165
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:27,000
 stvar,

166
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,860
 da će mene,

167
00:13:28,860 --> 00:13:29,840
 moj gospodin,

168
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:30,960
 ljubljeni Isus,

169
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:33,420
 promatrati,

170
00:13:33,420 --> 00:13:35,500
 ako hoćete suditi,

171
00:13:35,500 --> 00:13:36,660
 prosuđivati,

172
00:13:36,660 --> 00:13:38,440
 po mojoj savjesti,

173
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:40,120
 onakva kakva ona jest.

174
00:13:42,140 --> 00:13:43,760
 Bila ona skrupulozna ili okorjela?

175
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:45,220
 Po mojoj savjesti.

176
00:13:45,220 --> 00:13:50,500
 Ne po propisanoj savjesti kolektiviteta.

177
00:13:50,500 --> 00:13:52,080
 Onda nismo ništa.

178
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:57,820
 Zato se mi protiv toga moramo stalno pobuditi.

179
00:13:57,820 --> 00:13:59,580
 Zašto se uništava savjest?

180
00:13:59,580 --> 00:14:03,440
 Vidite, savjest je mogućnost biranja između dobra i zla.

181
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:07,980
 E sad, kad mi pobrkamo mogućnost biranja dobra i zla,

182
00:14:07,980 --> 00:14:08,880
 šta nastaje?

183
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:11,860
 Ono što žele zli ljudi da postoji.

184
00:14:11,980 --> 00:14:12,400
 kaos.

185
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:18,140
 Ima lišta gore nego kad u tebi vlada kaos,

186
00:14:18,140 --> 00:14:21,480
 da ti više ne znaš što je dobro, što je zlo.

187
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:23,120
 To je kaos.

188
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:27,820
 S čovjekom u kaosu je najlakše ovladati.

189
00:14:27,820 --> 00:14:33,740
 Stvori se košmar, kaos, napetost,

190
00:14:33,740 --> 00:14:38,120
 osjećaj straha, egzidencijalnog obstanka,

191
00:14:38,120 --> 00:14:41,740
 propadamo, sve se to tako u strahu,

192
00:14:41,820 --> 00:14:44,260
 nama nude lekcije.

193
00:14:44,260 --> 00:14:49,540
 A vidite, Isus stalno, sloboda, ljubav,

194
00:14:49,540 --> 00:14:53,220
 ne vojte se, ne dajte se ušutkati,

195
00:14:53,220 --> 00:14:56,240
 govorite, govorite.

196
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:02,500
 Dostojevski je dobro definirao jednu stvar.

197
00:15:02,500 --> 00:15:07,880
 kroz jednu riječ koju ja potpuno smatram

198
00:15:07,880 --> 00:15:12,400
 da je lingvistički ispravna,

199
00:15:12,400 --> 00:15:18,540
 ali misaono jako upitna i sotonistička.

200
00:15:18,700 --> 00:15:24,080
 to je tolerancija, ništa nije raširenije

201
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:29,280
 i zaposijelo ovu našu planetu kao ta poganska,

202
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:33,200
 to je konstrukt tolerancija.

203
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:37,540
 i pazite kad je davno Dostojevski Rus govorio, kaže,

204
00:15:37,540 --> 00:15:41,160
 tolerancija će doći do takve razine

205
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:44,380
 da će inteligentnim, razumnim ljudima

206
00:15:44,380 --> 00:15:47,580
 biti zabranjeno njihovo mišljenje

207
00:15:47,580 --> 00:15:51,580
 kako ne bi uvrijedili imbicile ili idiote.

208
00:15:53,580 --> 00:15:55,580
 To je danas na snagi.

209
00:15:55,580 --> 00:16:00,560
 Dakle, mi više ne smijemo izgovarati istine

210
00:16:00,560 --> 00:16:04,940
 jer to kao vrijeđa koga?

211
00:16:04,940 --> 00:16:07,360
 Imbicile? Idiote?

212
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:11,460
 Što bi tebe moglo vrijeđati

213
00:16:11,460 --> 00:16:15,060
 ako ja kažem da je ubojstvo djeteta

214
00:16:15,060 --> 00:16:16,760
 ispred kućenog praga,

215
00:16:16,760 --> 00:16:19,400
 u majičinom krevetu

216
00:16:19,400 --> 00:16:22,700
 ili u majičnoj utrobi jednako zločini zvjerstvo?

217
00:16:23,580 --> 00:16:28,480
 Zar je moguće da u 21. stoljeću modernog vremena

218
00:16:28,480 --> 00:16:30,740
 oni koji nama, kršćanama, prigovaraju

219
00:16:30,740 --> 00:16:32,620
 da živimo srednji vijek

220
00:16:32,620 --> 00:16:35,340
 treba objašnjavati

221
00:16:35,340 --> 00:16:37,000
 da je jednako

222
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:40,400
 ako ja, evo, mog framaša, bivšeg iz Posušija

223
00:16:40,400 --> 00:16:43,100
 udarim pleskom bilo ovdje

224
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:45,780
 bilo tu na sredini crkve ili tamo van crkve.

225
00:16:45,780 --> 00:16:51,620
 Pazite, to je to što je rekao Dostojenstvi.

226
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:53,940
 Dakle, to je taj idiotizam.

227
00:16:53,940 --> 00:16:58,700
 Nikakve razlike nema.

228
00:16:58,700 --> 00:17:04,160
 I dijete koje pogubiš u 12. godini života

229
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:06,640
 u 6. ili manje vrijedno, znaš, nije se reživilo

230
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:07,520
 ili dva mjeseca

231
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:09,960
 ili, ovdje, koliko, tri dana.

232
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:15,900
 Dok mi ne rješimo ta temeljna pitanja

233
00:17:15,900 --> 00:17:17,600
 dakle, sve će se govoriti

234
00:17:17,600 --> 00:17:18,620
 njih sve vrijedja.

235
00:17:18,620 --> 00:17:20,500
 Zašto ih vrijedja?

236
00:17:20,500 --> 00:17:21,980
 Vrijedja ih istina.

237
00:17:21,980 --> 00:17:24,440
 Jer džavao ne podnosi istinu.

238
00:17:29,580 --> 00:17:31,500
 U svu tu priču

239
00:17:31,500 --> 00:17:33,980
 uplela se

240
00:17:33,980 --> 00:17:35,940
 demokracija.

241
00:17:35,940 --> 00:17:40,520
 Demokracija vam je,

242
00:17:40,520 --> 00:17:42,540
 mnogi će reći to stručno,

243
00:17:42,540 --> 00:17:46,940
 najmanje loš oblik vladanja.

244
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:48,180
 Znači, ne kazaš istad,

245
00:17:48,180 --> 00:17:48,780
 i oni koji

246
00:17:48,780 --> 00:17:51,020
 najpozitivnije govore,

247
00:17:51,020 --> 00:17:51,580
 kažu da je to

248
00:17:51,580 --> 00:17:53,840
 najmanje loš oblik vladanja.

249
00:17:55,340 --> 00:17:57,560
 I dobro je jedan mudra čovjek napisao

250
00:17:57,560 --> 00:17:59,640
 demokracija je kad ovce

251
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:01,920
 biraju koji će ih vuk pojesti.

252
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:08,420
 Predizborno je vrijeme,

253
00:18:08,420 --> 00:18:10,500
 ne bi se u to htio mješati,

254
00:18:10,500 --> 00:18:11,420
 jer

255
00:18:11,420 --> 00:18:14,420
 nisam sretan.

256
00:18:14,420 --> 00:18:16,620
 Nisam sretan.

257
00:18:16,620 --> 00:18:18,820
 E, to tisto kad ti dođeš

258
00:18:18,820 --> 00:18:20,420
 na tržnicu,

259
00:18:20,420 --> 00:18:21,120
 vidiš ono,

260
00:18:21,120 --> 00:18:24,480
 ona rajčica od prije 20 dana,

261
00:18:25,020 --> 00:18:25,860
 paprike, vece,

262
00:18:25,860 --> 00:18:26,220
 ono,

263
00:18:26,220 --> 00:18:27,180
 smriškale,

264
00:18:27,180 --> 00:18:28,700
 kapula,

265
00:18:28,700 --> 00:18:30,220
 Bože te sačuvaj,

266
00:18:30,220 --> 00:18:31,180
 krompir,

267
00:18:31,180 --> 00:18:32,660
 već od njega iznikla ona klica

268
00:18:32,660 --> 00:18:33,320
 za dogodine.

269
00:18:33,320 --> 00:18:35,540
 Nema šta izabrati,

270
00:18:35,540 --> 00:18:36,040
 odlaziš.

271
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:40,740
 Naravno da ćemo mi kao kršćani,

272
00:18:40,740 --> 00:18:41,940
 ja ću načerno reći,

273
00:18:41,940 --> 00:18:43,320
 birati manje zlo.

274
00:18:43,320 --> 00:18:45,240
 To je sve što vam može reći

275
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:46,160
 ovaj čiko ovdje.

276
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:49,220
 Ja vam ne mogu ovdje

277
00:18:49,220 --> 00:18:50,400
 doslovno reći,

278
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:52,380
 osim kad vi znate neke pojedince

279
00:18:52,380 --> 00:18:54,000
 u vašem selu, gradu i drugdje,

280
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:54,820
 to je druga priča,

281
00:18:54,820 --> 00:18:55,980
 ali što se događa,

282
00:18:55,980 --> 00:18:56,340
 pazite,

283
00:18:56,340 --> 00:18:57,980
 danas sam baš s nekim čovjekom

284
00:18:57,980 --> 00:18:59,080
 analizirao liste

285
00:18:59,080 --> 00:19:01,700
 i kako se to mudro odrađuje.

286
00:19:01,700 --> 00:19:02,880
 Ja gledam listu,

287
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:04,900
 koliko je 14 ili mora biti ljudi tamo je,

288
00:19:04,900 --> 00:19:06,480
 osoba sad ljudi,

289
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:06,960
 koliko je,

290
00:19:06,960 --> 00:19:07,340
 Bog zna.

291
00:19:08,740 --> 00:19:16,020
 14 je njih tamo poredano i kako je to mudrijaško lukavstvo,

292
00:19:16,020 --> 00:19:19,440
 stave je dva, tri stvarno čestita čovjeka.

293
00:19:20,620 --> 00:19:21,820
 dva, tri čestita,

294
00:19:21,820 --> 00:19:23,500
 kao na vlakušu.

295
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:25,720
 Ali oni doli 12,

296
00:19:25,720 --> 00:19:26,880
 Bože te sačuvaj,

297
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:29,140
 nitko ih za zeta ne bi htio.

298
00:19:29,140 --> 00:19:31,900
 Ali sad šta se događa?

299
00:19:31,900 --> 00:19:33,560
 Ti sada računaš,

300
00:19:33,560 --> 00:19:33,820
 evo,

301
00:19:33,820 --> 00:19:35,100
 dobar je moj marin,

302
00:19:35,100 --> 00:19:36,960
 pa moram za marna izbatinat čovjek,

303
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:38,080
 pa kako neću za nj.

304
00:19:38,080 --> 00:19:39,640
 Ali kad ja okružim marina,

305
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:42,780
 a ja okružio i ovih drugih 13.

306
00:19:42,780 --> 00:19:46,400
 Kako je to smišljeno,

307
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:50,800
 kako je to ta demokracija varka i laž.

308
00:19:50,800 --> 00:19:52,780
 Laž.

309
00:19:52,780 --> 00:19:54,620
 Ali evo,

310
00:19:54,620 --> 00:19:56,540
 birati nam je manje zlo.

311
00:19:56,540 --> 00:20:02,620
 Vatikanskim koncilu Gaudium S5 kaže broj 74.

312
00:20:02,620 --> 00:20:06,400
 Ako vlast prelazi nadležnosti

313
00:20:06,400 --> 00:20:09,400
 i počinje tlačiti,

314
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:13,560
 onda je obrana nužnost.

315
00:20:13,560 --> 00:20:15,240
 Nužnost.

316
00:20:15,240 --> 00:20:21,260
 Ali ovo počinje sada zbilja tlačenje,

317
00:20:21,260 --> 00:20:25,520
 prelazi se svaka nadležnost,

318
00:20:25,520 --> 00:20:30,820
 gdje se ne želi služiti,

319
00:20:30,820 --> 00:20:32,420
 da ne kaže vladati,

320
00:20:32,420 --> 00:20:35,080
 nego preodgajati narod.

321
00:20:35,080 --> 00:20:38,820
 Nas se želi preodgajati,

322
00:20:38,820 --> 00:20:41,980
 jer nismo dovoljno dobri građani.

323
00:20:43,420 --> 00:20:46,000
 neki dan čujem od jedne onaj,

324
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:48,440
 tako, to je polusvijet,

325
00:20:48,440 --> 00:20:49,480
 nekakva tu,

326
00:20:49,480 --> 00:20:52,240
 koja ali ona ne zna, nije, nije važno ime,

327
00:20:52,240 --> 00:20:56,460
 ovo kad se dogodilo ubojstvo u Zagrebu,

328
00:20:56,460 --> 00:20:58,040
 i prije ih je bilo,

329
00:20:58,040 --> 00:20:59,260
 nisu mediji javljali,

330
00:20:59,260 --> 00:21:01,480
 i svugdje je toga bilo,

331
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:02,500
 nije se javljalo.

332
00:21:04,040 --> 00:21:05,960
 po meni se ni danas, to ne treba javljati.

333
00:21:05,960 --> 00:21:09,120
 Šta mi imamo od toga?

334
00:21:09,120 --> 00:21:12,320
 I ona tamo priča, kaže,

335
00:21:12,320 --> 00:21:15,560
 nužno je uvesti u škole građanski odgoj,

336
00:21:15,560 --> 00:21:18,320
 jer evo, događaju se obojstvo.

337
00:21:22,360 --> 00:21:23,900
 Čujete li vi šta, šta ja govorim?

338
00:21:23,900 --> 00:21:25,540
 No, ne da nam ja da čujem,

339
00:21:25,540 --> 00:21:27,580
 nego, ja nako gledam tu žensku,

340
00:21:27,580 --> 00:21:30,660
 ja gledam tu žensku, pa čekaj,

341
00:21:30,660 --> 00:21:33,960
 i ona veli da će građanski odgoj

342
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:38,060
 smanjiti ubojstva u Zagrebu.

343
00:21:38,060 --> 00:21:42,360
 Tu bi Matan iz Prosijaka i Sinova rekao,

344
00:21:42,360 --> 00:21:44,640
 pametju draču začudila.

345
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:50,820
 Ali to ide,

346
00:21:51,120 --> 00:21:52,440
 u središnjem dnevniku

347
00:21:52,440 --> 00:21:54,840
 i takav polusvijet se nametnu

348
00:21:54,840 --> 00:21:56,480
 u koji nama neku priču priča

349
00:21:56,480 --> 00:21:58,060
 i netko će na to pasti.

350
00:21:58,060 --> 00:22:02,600
 Umisla da rekla, kućni odgoj,

351
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:04,080
 odgoj roditelja,

352
00:22:04,080 --> 00:22:07,020
 odgoj u tom tvom vrtiću

353
00:22:07,020 --> 00:22:07,900
 gdje ti ne daš

354
00:22:07,900 --> 00:22:10,540
 zahvaljivati Bogu za darovani kruh.

355
00:22:10,540 --> 00:22:14,300
 E to je to, preodgoj.

356
00:22:14,300 --> 00:22:16,520
 Oni nas žele preodgajati,

357
00:22:16,520 --> 00:22:18,700
 jer mi kao nismo dobri građani.

358
00:22:18,700 --> 00:22:20,520
 Kakve oni žele građane dobre?

359
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:21,160
 Bez Boga.

360
00:22:21,160 --> 00:22:25,380
 Mi smo dobri samo ako smo bez Boga.

361
00:22:25,380 --> 00:22:28,580
 To je to stvaranje novog svjetskog poredka.

362
00:22:28,580 --> 00:22:31,020
 Ljudi bez Boga,

363
00:22:31,020 --> 00:22:33,620
 ljudi bez identiteta,

364
00:22:33,620 --> 00:22:36,100
 ljudi bez svojih korijena,

365
00:22:36,100 --> 00:22:39,180
 ljudi bez pripadnosti

366
00:22:39,180 --> 00:22:41,960
 i lako je s njima manipulirati.

367
00:22:41,960 --> 00:22:47,040
 O tome bi vam mogao dugo,

368
00:22:47,040 --> 00:22:50,440
 ali ne mogu jer morat ćemo ovaj sat mi čovjek dao.

369
00:22:53,880 --> 00:22:56,060
 šta nas jedino može izliječiti?

370
00:22:56,060 --> 00:22:58,800
 O tome sam pisao dugi esej,

371
00:22:58,800 --> 00:22:59,660
 to je u mojej knjizi,

372
00:22:59,660 --> 00:23:01,020
 to je meritokracija.

373
00:23:01,020 --> 00:23:03,780
 Dakle, jedini sustav

374
00:23:03,780 --> 00:23:05,280
 koji je ispravan,

375
00:23:05,280 --> 00:23:06,600
 nije demokracija,

376
00:23:06,600 --> 00:23:08,420
 nego meritokracija.

377
00:23:09,300 --> 00:23:11,280
 meritum riječ znači vrijednost,

378
00:23:11,280 --> 00:23:13,020
 kretein vladati.

379
00:23:13,020 --> 00:23:14,860
 Ejte,

380
00:23:14,860 --> 00:23:17,920
 mi imamo o blizu i ovo kretein.

381
00:23:20,300 --> 00:23:21,760
 Vi stvarno kužite.

382
00:23:21,760 --> 00:23:26,880
 Nisam ja kriv ovi kuže.

383
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:31,020
 Dakle, što znači meritokracija?

384
00:23:31,020 --> 00:23:33,400
 Propitivati,

385
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:34,380
 pa vidite mi sada

386
00:23:34,380 --> 00:23:36,300
 za izbore nikad ne propitujem,

387
00:23:36,300 --> 00:23:37,300
 oni nas propituju.

388
00:23:37,300 --> 00:23:40,040
 Pa oni propituju o našim stvarima,

389
00:23:40,040 --> 00:23:41,040
 njih se pita o neki,

390
00:23:41,040 --> 00:23:42,920
 ali mi ne propitujemo kandidati.

391
00:23:42,920 --> 00:23:46,560
 Je li se igdje,

392
00:23:46,560 --> 00:23:48,540
 evo, ja možda nisam pratio,

393
00:23:48,540 --> 00:23:49,420
 ja ne pratim to sada,

394
00:23:49,420 --> 00:23:50,180
 ja sam inače,

395
00:23:50,300 --> 00:23:52,440
 ovih dana

396
00:23:52,440 --> 00:23:55,220
 ne pratim ništa te kampanje i to,

397
00:23:55,220 --> 00:23:56,160
 i tako.

398
00:23:56,160 --> 00:23:57,140
 Ali sam prije pratio,

399
00:23:57,140 --> 00:23:58,540
 jer sam na fakultetu,

400
00:23:58,540 --> 00:23:59,900
 profesor te neke struke,

401
00:23:59,900 --> 00:24:00,780
 pa moram malo.

402
00:24:00,780 --> 00:24:02,240
 Ali ne pratim sad ove ništa.

403
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:05,620
 Jeste li vi gdje čuli?

404
00:24:05,620 --> 00:24:08,580
 Je li se jednog kandata pitalo,

405
00:24:08,580 --> 00:24:10,180
 živiš li u sakramentalnom braku?

406
00:24:10,180 --> 00:24:11,820
 Je li ko čuo?

407
00:24:11,820 --> 00:24:15,320
 Uvecaj sine duha svetog vam.

408
00:24:15,320 --> 00:24:16,520
 Stvarno nije.

409
00:24:16,520 --> 00:24:18,860
 Čovječe Boži,

410
00:24:18,960 --> 00:24:21,100
 to je čak u Poganoj Americi

411
00:24:21,100 --> 00:24:21,940
 važno pitanje.

412
00:24:21,940 --> 00:24:23,880
 Tamo nema šanse

413
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:24,820
 da budeš,

414
00:24:24,820 --> 00:24:27,080
 ako ti nije uredan bračni život,

415
00:24:27,080 --> 00:24:27,800
 da uspiješ.

416
00:24:31,240 --> 00:24:32,920
 je li se u nas pita,

417
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:34,000
 evo što ste vi pitali,

418
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:35,600
 zaokruživaćete neke te,

419
00:24:35,600 --> 00:24:37,100
 gospodje, ljude,

420
00:24:37,100 --> 00:24:40,000
 u kakvom ti živiš braku?

421
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:42,440
 Imaš li ljubavnicu?

422
00:24:42,440 --> 00:24:46,340
 Gdje su ti djeca?

423
00:24:46,340 --> 00:24:47,120
 Poštuju li te?

424
00:24:47,120 --> 00:24:48,380
 Imaš li obitelj?

425
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:52,180
 Umjesto da mi njih propitujemo

426
00:24:52,180 --> 00:24:52,860
 kad date,

427
00:24:52,860 --> 00:24:54,140
 oni nas propituju.

428
00:24:54,140 --> 00:24:56,100
 Vite,

429
00:24:56,100 --> 00:24:57,180
 opet govorim,

430
00:24:57,180 --> 00:24:58,460
 stalno protoslovlja

431
00:24:58,460 --> 00:24:59,320
 paradoksi

432
00:24:59,320 --> 00:25:01,000
 ovog našeg ludog svijeta.

433
00:25:02,620 --> 00:25:03,920
 Znači, nigdje nema razgovora

434
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:06,660
 o tome jesu li to čestiti ljudi,

435
00:25:06,660 --> 00:25:08,680
 jesu li provjereni u radu,

436
00:25:08,680 --> 00:25:09,820
 imaju li vrednote,

437
00:25:09,820 --> 00:25:11,080
 to je to meritokracija.

438
00:25:11,080 --> 00:25:12,260
 Znači, meritokracija je

439
00:25:12,260 --> 00:25:13,840
 najsposobniji

440
00:25:13,840 --> 00:25:17,780
 sa najvećim učinkom IQ,

441
00:25:17,780 --> 00:25:19,520
 inteligencijom,

442
00:25:19,520 --> 00:25:20,440
 znanjima,

443
00:25:20,440 --> 00:25:22,640
 sposobnostima i kompetencijama,

444
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:24,760
 a na dasve vrednotama

445
00:25:24,760 --> 00:25:25,880
 mogu tek vladati.

446
00:25:25,880 --> 00:25:27,580
 To je meritokracija.

447
00:25:27,580 --> 00:25:31,740
 To je meritokracija.

448
00:25:32,620 --> 00:25:37,200
 Zato

449
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:39,780
 Einstein kaže

450
00:25:39,780 --> 00:25:40,720
 svijet nije loš

451
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:43,060
 zbog ljudi koji su loši,

452
00:25:43,060 --> 00:25:44,120
 nego zbog dobri

453
00:25:44,120 --> 00:25:46,680
 koji su ravnodušni.

454
00:25:46,680 --> 00:25:49,960
 Mi smo krivi.

455
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:51,540
 Ja, prvi.

456
00:25:51,540 --> 00:25:52,700
 Mi smo krivi,

457
00:25:52,700 --> 00:25:53,680
 ravnodušni,

458
00:25:53,680 --> 00:25:55,540
 jer znamo

459
00:25:55,540 --> 00:25:57,860
 pogeti glavu

460
00:25:57,860 --> 00:26:00,760
 i progutati različite knedle

461
00:26:00,760 --> 00:26:03,220
 u ime nekakvih ciljeva

462
00:26:03,220 --> 00:26:05,480
 koje nitko nikada nije nigdje definirao.

463
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:06,340
 Kojih ciljeva?

464
00:26:08,340 --> 00:26:11,660
 To je ovo, nisam ni pristaša da mora Hrvatska obstati bilo kakva.

465
00:26:11,660 --> 00:26:13,580
 Meni treba samo Božija Hrvatska.

466
00:26:13,580 --> 00:26:16,840
 Ta priča,

467
00:26:16,840 --> 00:26:19,480
 a oni će uništit domovinu,

468
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,120
 ona će ovo,

469
00:26:20,120 --> 00:26:21,540
 sve to ja razumijem,

470
00:26:21,540 --> 00:26:22,480
 čuvamo domovinu,

471
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:22,920
 za nju su,

472
00:26:22,920 --> 00:26:24,140
 nju nisu oni stvorili,

473
00:26:24,140 --> 00:26:24,920
 ne mogu je ni uništit.

474
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:26,620
 ne bojite se.

475
00:26:26,620 --> 00:26:30,140
 Ovu domovinu nisu oni stvarali,

476
00:26:30,140 --> 00:26:31,100
 neće ni uštavati.

477
00:26:31,100 --> 00:26:33,360
 Ne u krv naših branitelja.

478
00:26:33,360 --> 00:26:35,860
 Branitelji naših.

479
00:26:35,860 --> 00:26:37,320
 Meni je uvijek ostalo,

480
00:26:37,320 --> 00:26:38,740
 to ću sad pričati uz put,

481
00:26:38,740 --> 00:26:40,180
 gdje mi dade ovaj sad.

482
00:26:40,180 --> 00:26:41,020
 E, slušaj.

483
00:26:41,020 --> 00:26:44,140
 Ja u Londonu držim seminar,

484
00:26:44,140 --> 00:26:46,400
 tamo jedan katolik organizira,

485
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:47,160
 Paul Spencer,

486
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:50,100
 i ujutro imam vremena,

487
00:26:50,100 --> 00:26:51,840
 kao jutro s na činomericu,

488
00:26:51,840 --> 00:26:52,760
 kad sam prošetao

489
00:26:52,760 --> 00:26:55,380
 i vidio što rade zagrebčani,

490
00:26:55,380 --> 00:26:57,480
 neću vam sakazati što sam zamijetio.

491
00:26:57,480 --> 00:27:01,340
 E, ja vidim tamo jedna prekrasna zgrada,

492
00:27:01,340 --> 00:27:03,040
 vidim, nije hotel,

493
00:27:03,040 --> 00:27:04,600
 ali nešto je slično.

494
00:27:04,600 --> 00:27:09,480
 I prekrasne klupe ispred tog hotela,

495
00:27:09,480 --> 00:27:11,060
 smještaja, ne znam kako bi razlog.

496
00:27:11,060 --> 00:27:12,760
 Ja prilazim malo nakon šutke,

497
00:27:12,760 --> 00:27:13,980
 točno London.

498
00:27:13,980 --> 00:27:18,860
 Vidim, ovako jedan čovjek nema noge,

499
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:20,700
 drugi tamo u kolici,

500
00:27:20,700 --> 00:27:22,780
 treći onako malo hoda,

501
00:27:22,780 --> 00:27:23,420
 ono, znaš.

502
00:27:23,420 --> 00:27:25,380
 I snimao i vidi neku ima.

503
00:27:25,380 --> 00:27:27,800
 Ja raču na neka bolnica,

504
00:27:27,800 --> 00:27:28,820
 pa pohodili ih.

505
00:27:28,820 --> 00:27:30,800
 Pazite šta, da vam skratim.

506
00:27:30,800 --> 00:27:34,200
 Ja pitam ovoga šta je u ovdje,

507
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:34,800
 možete reći.

508
00:27:34,800 --> 00:27:37,460
 Ovo, kaže, ovo je, kaže,

509
00:27:37,460 --> 00:27:39,220
 kako bi rekao,

510
00:27:39,220 --> 00:27:41,940
 dnevni boravak za njihove ratnike,

511
00:27:41,940 --> 00:27:43,940
 branitelje, vojnike.

512
00:27:43,940 --> 00:27:46,160
 Dobro.

513
00:27:46,160 --> 00:27:47,880
 Pa šta vi, reko, radite?

514
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:49,020
 ste njima, brat, rođenike.

515
00:27:49,020 --> 00:27:49,820
 Ne, ne, ne, kaže.

516
00:27:49,820 --> 00:27:51,920
 Mi smo plaćeni od države

517
00:27:51,920 --> 00:27:53,340
 i to jako dobro.

518
00:27:53,340 --> 00:27:55,660
 Da se s njima družimo,

519
00:27:55,660 --> 00:27:57,920
 da im budemo na uslijde

520
00:27:57,920 --> 00:27:59,200
 ako treba donijeti novine,

521
00:27:59,200 --> 00:28:00,700
 s njima idemo na piće,

522
00:28:00,700 --> 00:28:02,960
 ako treba odvezamo ih liječniku,

523
00:28:02,960 --> 00:28:04,080
 provodimo s njima dan,

524
00:28:04,080 --> 00:28:04,900
 da ih nije dosadno,

525
00:28:04,900 --> 00:28:06,620
 da nisu prepušteni sami sebi,

526
00:28:06,620 --> 00:28:08,180
 nego da im pokažemo ljubav.

527
00:28:08,180 --> 00:28:09,880
 Pa di su, reko,

528
00:28:09,880 --> 00:28:10,280
 branuli,

529
00:28:10,280 --> 00:28:11,080
 tadan, tamo bio,

530
00:28:11,080 --> 00:28:12,520
 to je ono kad je bila priča,

531
00:28:12,520 --> 00:28:13,800
 da sam ja bio kod Tonja Blera,

532
00:28:13,800 --> 00:28:14,220
 to je,

533
00:28:14,220 --> 00:28:18,100
 pa se onda bratira katoličanstvo.

534
00:28:18,100 --> 00:28:18,500
 E,

535
00:28:18,500 --> 00:28:20,120
 ja velim pa,

536
00:28:20,120 --> 00:28:21,960
 gdje su branuli,

537
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:22,940
 šta su branuli?

538
00:28:22,940 --> 00:28:25,520
 O, šta su kad je došli iz Iraka?

539
00:28:25,520 --> 00:28:28,000
 Ko su branuli u Iraku?

540
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:28,960
 Svi mi znao.

541
00:28:29,260 --> 00:28:29,620
 Pazite,

542
00:28:29,620 --> 00:28:31,440
 oni svoje vojnike,

543
00:28:31,440 --> 00:28:34,880
 koji nisu u Engleskoj branuli Englesku,

544
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:36,140
 nego išli

545
00:28:36,140 --> 00:28:39,240
 outsourcing.

546
00:28:39,240 --> 00:28:46,100
 Oni drže na pijedestalu kao velikane,

547
00:28:46,100 --> 00:28:47,420
 a mi naše

548
00:28:47,420 --> 00:28:50,300
 gurnuli iz institucija,

549
00:28:50,300 --> 00:28:51,540
 pazite, kažu ne ilustracija,

550
00:28:51,540 --> 00:28:52,740
 Hrvatsko je bila ilustracija,

551
00:28:52,740 --> 00:28:55,480
 udba i komunjare su ilustrirale nas

552
00:28:55,480 --> 00:28:56,480
 od naših domoljuba,

553
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:57,320
 branitelja,

554
00:28:58,060 --> 00:28:58,940
 intelektualaca,

555
00:28:58,940 --> 00:28:59,980
 koji misle Hrvatski.

556
00:28:59,980 --> 00:29:00,840
 Bila ilustracija,

557
00:29:00,840 --> 00:29:01,760
 samo ova njihova.

558
00:29:01,760 --> 00:29:03,360
 Pazite,

559
00:29:03,360 --> 00:29:03,760
 koja je to,

560
00:29:03,760 --> 00:29:04,240
 Džavolska,

561
00:29:04,240 --> 00:29:05,040
 bila podvala,

562
00:29:05,040 --> 00:29:06,060
 oni lijepo,

563
00:29:06,060 --> 00:29:07,740
 ljude koji su stvorili državu,

564
00:29:07,740 --> 00:29:09,260
 to isto ti napraviš kuću,

565
00:29:09,260 --> 00:29:10,740
 završiš kuću,

566
00:29:10,740 --> 00:29:11,900
 na njoj se znojio,

567
00:29:11,900 --> 00:29:13,380
 dva puta se ozlijedio,

568
00:29:13,380 --> 00:29:14,820
 daska ti pala na glavu,

569
00:29:14,820 --> 00:29:16,420
 sve uložio

570
00:29:16,420 --> 00:29:17,780
 i kad se završio kuću,

571
00:29:17,780 --> 00:29:18,520
 oni te kažu,

572
00:29:18,520 --> 00:29:20,700
 aj ti znaš,

573
00:29:20,700 --> 00:29:21,880
 tamo nek drugo stanu

574
00:29:21,880 --> 00:29:22,380
 i ovo je nama.

575
00:29:23,140 --> 00:29:24,020
 Oni tebe istirali

576
00:29:24,020 --> 00:29:25,020
 iz vlastite kuće

577
00:29:25,020 --> 00:29:26,060
 za koju ti krvario.

578
00:29:26,060 --> 00:29:27,420
 To se Hrvatsko je dogodilo,

579
00:29:27,420 --> 00:29:28,260
 zato nema blagoslova.

580
00:29:28,260 --> 00:29:30,560
 Dok vidiš u Londonu,

581
00:29:30,560 --> 00:29:31,460
 oni svoje,

582
00:29:31,460 --> 00:29:32,980
 oni su biti agresori.

583
00:29:35,740 --> 00:29:37,760
 drže do njih kao do velikana,

584
00:29:37,760 --> 00:29:39,660
 a mi branili, krvarli,

585
00:29:39,660 --> 00:29:40,580
 naši branitelji,

586
00:29:40,580 --> 00:29:41,840
 oni nama, šta,

587
00:29:41,840 --> 00:29:43,520
 jednici skončavaju

588
00:29:43,520 --> 00:29:45,600
 na različite načine u zemlju.

589
00:29:45,600 --> 00:29:48,060
 Ja se ne bojim

590
00:29:48,060 --> 00:29:49,700
 za domovinu.

591
00:29:49,700 --> 00:29:51,760
 Dokle goti jedan od njih

592
00:29:51,760 --> 00:29:52,560
 je na ovoj zemlji,

593
00:29:52,560 --> 00:29:53,600
 jedan dostaje.

594
00:29:53,600 --> 00:29:55,380
 Jedan svjedok,

595
00:29:55,380 --> 00:29:57,520
 a imamo ih puno,

596
00:29:57,520 --> 00:29:58,120
 Bogu hvala.

597
00:29:58,120 --> 00:29:59,760
 Ne trebamo se brinuti.

598
00:29:59,760 --> 00:30:02,760
 Tu nema dileme.

599
00:30:04,840 --> 00:30:06,140
 samo mi se moramo hrabljiti.

600
00:30:06,140 --> 00:30:08,280
 Kad je Hrušćov,

601
00:30:08,280 --> 00:30:09,380
 čuli ste vi za njega,

602
00:30:09,380 --> 00:30:11,120
 naslijedio je on Stalina.

603
00:30:11,120 --> 00:30:16,120
 I govori on tamo u njihovoj dumi,

604
00:30:16,120 --> 00:30:18,140
 ti je centralni komitet,

605
00:30:18,140 --> 00:30:19,660
 Sovjet i tako dalje,

606
00:30:19,660 --> 00:30:21,400
 drži on govor.

607
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:26,660
 I on govori protiv Stalina.

608
00:30:26,660 --> 00:30:29,720
 Kako je bilo zla,

609
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:31,800
 koje se ne smije više ponavlja te priče.

610
00:30:31,800 --> 00:30:34,240
 U tom jedan dolje u dumi viknu,

611
00:30:34,440 --> 00:30:37,300
 što ste šutijali dok je on bio živ?

612
00:30:37,300 --> 00:30:39,620
 Stade Hrušćov zgovorom.

613
00:30:39,620 --> 00:30:40,980
 Oprostite,

614
00:30:40,980 --> 00:30:42,100
 drug,

615
00:30:42,100 --> 00:30:43,060
 ko je to rekao?

616
00:30:43,060 --> 00:30:44,640
 Ustanite da vidim ko je to rekao.

617
00:30:44,640 --> 00:30:47,140
 Nitko ni ustao.

618
00:30:47,140 --> 00:30:49,020
 I on uzgovara,

619
00:30:49,020 --> 00:30:49,980
 eto.

620
00:30:49,980 --> 00:30:52,840
 Sad si dobio odgovor.

621
00:30:52,840 --> 00:30:54,500
 Takav sam bio i ja,

622
00:30:54,500 --> 00:30:55,960
 dok je Stalina ovdje govorio.

623
00:30:58,840 --> 00:30:59,560
 šutio sam.

624
00:30:59,560 --> 00:31:02,200
 Pogio sam glavu.

625
00:31:02,200 --> 00:31:03,400
 Sram me.

626
00:31:03,400 --> 00:31:05,980
 Evo ti sad meni govoriš,

627
00:31:05,980 --> 00:31:07,060
 nisim o hrabrosti,

628
00:31:07,060 --> 00:31:07,700
 ne ustao ti reći,

629
00:31:07,700 --> 00:31:09,060
 ja sam rekao gospodne,

630
00:31:09,060 --> 00:31:10,240
 ili druže Hrušćov,

631
00:31:10,240 --> 00:31:12,220
 što ste šutili dok je Stalin

632
00:31:12,220 --> 00:31:14,020
 slao ljude u smrt i na Sibir.

633
00:31:16,020 --> 00:31:17,320
 Bio sam kada je kukavica,

634
00:31:17,320 --> 00:31:19,040
 oko ti sad koji nešto ustaneš.

635
00:31:19,040 --> 00:31:21,060
 To je nama problem.

636
00:31:21,060 --> 00:31:23,840
 Mi moramo ustati,

637
00:31:23,840 --> 00:31:25,240
 izložiti se.

638
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:26,260
 Model.

639
00:31:26,260 --> 00:31:28,800
 Imamo sputa križa,

640
00:31:28,800 --> 00:31:31,400
 Šimu Cirenac,

641
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:32,060
 Veronika,

642
00:31:32,060 --> 00:31:35,260
 žene koje prate Isusa,

643
00:31:35,260 --> 00:31:37,180
 Ivan Ljubljeni učenik

644
00:31:37,180 --> 00:31:38,820
 koji jedini nije pobjegao.

645
00:31:38,820 --> 00:31:43,340
 Zato evo za kraj,

646
00:31:43,340 --> 00:31:44,600
 dragi moji prijatelji,

647
00:31:46,020 --> 00:31:47,980
 mi smo dužni opominjati.

648
00:31:47,980 --> 00:31:49,280
 Ezekijel prorok kaže,

649
00:31:49,280 --> 00:31:51,280
 ti službeniče Boži,

650
00:31:51,280 --> 00:31:52,980
 ako ne opomeneš grešnike,

651
00:31:52,980 --> 00:31:55,000
 oni će zbog svojih grijeha

652
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:55,960
 završiti u paklu.

653
00:31:55,960 --> 00:31:58,760
 Ali ti koji ih nisi opomenuo,

654
00:31:58,760 --> 00:32:01,180
 e o tebe će Bog iskati duše njihove,

655
00:32:01,180 --> 00:32:02,420
 ti ćeš isto završiti u paklu.

656
00:32:02,420 --> 00:32:04,080
 Vidite koja odgovorna svećenika.

657
00:32:04,080 --> 00:32:08,800
 I nama žele oduzeti tu našu obvezu

658
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:12,760
 da ja ovom narodu grešnom

659
00:32:12,760 --> 00:32:14,120
 i preljubničkom naraštoju

660
00:32:14,120 --> 00:32:15,120
 kažem istinu.

661
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:16,980
 Jer ako ja ne kažem,

662
00:32:16,980 --> 00:32:19,200
 moja duša će završiti u ognju paklu do me.

663
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:20,540
 To Božja riječ kaže.

664
00:32:20,540 --> 00:32:23,900
 Zato hrabrite se.

665
00:32:23,900 --> 00:32:26,120
 Evojte,

666
00:32:26,120 --> 00:32:27,400
 znate,

667
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:30,640
 ja mislim da ćemo na kraju života

668
00:32:30,640 --> 00:32:32,000
 i sami ste sebe našli,

669
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:33,440
 najviše sebi prigovoriti

670
00:32:33,440 --> 00:32:35,420
 koji nismo bili odlučni

671
00:32:35,420 --> 00:32:36,440
 i hrabri.

672
00:32:37,180 --> 00:32:38,000
 neka mi kaza,

673
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:39,860
 ne treba nama to.

674
00:32:39,860 --> 00:32:43,840
 Ne neki fundamentalizam gdje ovi viču

675
00:32:43,840 --> 00:32:47,240
 nekakve parole po cestama

676
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:49,520
 drugih nekakvih jerskih zajednica.

677
00:32:49,520 --> 00:32:50,660
 Ne, mi to nismo.

678
00:32:51,760 --> 00:32:53,500
 Duh sveti je blag i lahor,

679
00:32:53,500 --> 00:32:55,100
 ali koji stalno piri,

680
00:32:55,100 --> 00:32:58,580
 koji stalno govori,

681
00:32:58,580 --> 00:33:00,380
 puše gdje hoće i kad hoće.

682
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:02,940
 Mi da imamo,

683
00:33:02,940 --> 00:33:03,980
 u mojoj emisiji,

684
00:33:03,980 --> 00:33:04,920
 pauna reče,

685
00:33:04,920 --> 00:33:06,460
 tri posto.

686
00:33:06,460 --> 00:33:08,900
 Tri posto da imamo,

687
00:33:08,900 --> 00:33:09,460
 mi kaže,

688
00:33:09,460 --> 00:33:12,300
 čestitih katolika Hrvata,

689
00:33:12,300 --> 00:33:13,300
 mi bi procijetali.

690
00:33:13,300 --> 00:33:14,080
 Tri posto.

691
00:33:14,080 --> 00:33:18,540
 Ja sam smanjio na jedan i pol posto.

692
00:33:18,540 --> 00:33:22,280
 Na jedan i pol posto.

693
00:33:22,280 --> 00:33:25,180
 Ja vam mogu nabrojiti,

694
00:33:25,180 --> 00:33:26,060
 ako hoćete i mene,

695
00:33:26,060 --> 00:33:27,120
 ali neću sad ovim čitati.

696
00:33:27,120 --> 00:33:28,800
 Šta mi imamo u Hrvatskoj?

697
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:30,640
 Mi smo se sveli na

698
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:32,560
 dvadeset, trideset nekih imena

699
00:33:32,560 --> 00:33:34,180
 koji nešto nam mogu reći

700
00:33:34,180 --> 00:33:35,440
 i od koji možemo nešto čuti.

701
00:33:35,440 --> 00:33:37,640
 Sve drugo je protokol,

702
00:33:37,640 --> 00:33:38,760
 protokol, protokol.

703
00:33:38,760 --> 00:33:40,040
 Obavljanje forme.

704
00:33:40,040 --> 00:33:42,740
 Zato su nam srca hladna.

705
00:33:42,740 --> 00:33:45,120
 Zato nema plodova.

706
00:33:45,120 --> 00:33:47,460
 Zato nema plodova.

707
00:33:47,460 --> 00:33:48,460
 Obavljamo protokol.

708
00:33:48,460 --> 00:33:51,280
 Ništa se ne događa.

709
00:33:51,280 --> 00:33:53,200
 Sve mi to odradimo fino.

710
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:55,920
 Nije malo,

711
00:33:55,920 --> 00:33:56,780
 jedan i pol posto.

712
00:33:56,780 --> 00:33:58,780
 Nije malo.

713
00:34:00,060 --> 00:34:00,560
 Da mi imamo

714
00:34:00,560 --> 00:34:01,820
 toliko

715
00:34:01,820 --> 00:34:03,360
 onih koji su spremni

716
00:34:03,360 --> 00:34:04,440
 danas posvjedočiti,

717
00:34:04,440 --> 00:34:06,860
 svoje živote

718
00:34:06,860 --> 00:34:07,720
 založiti,

719
00:34:07,720 --> 00:34:08,860
 koji su spremni

720
00:34:08,860 --> 00:34:11,560
 inteligenciju i dar Boži

721
00:34:11,560 --> 00:34:12,300
 upotrijebiti

722
00:34:12,300 --> 00:34:13,800
 za ono što je Božija stvar,

723
00:34:13,800 --> 00:34:15,280
 mi bi smo svi procvjetali.

724
00:34:15,280 --> 00:34:17,720
 Hvako ćemo se

725
00:34:17,720 --> 00:34:18,600
 bucarati,

726
00:34:18,600 --> 00:34:19,520
 kao što kaže tamo

727
00:34:19,520 --> 00:34:20,000
 Ilija,

728
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:20,220
 kaže,

729
00:34:20,220 --> 00:34:21,580
 ba dokle ćete lutati

730
00:34:21,580 --> 00:34:22,520
 na dvije strane.

731
00:34:22,520 --> 00:34:25,100
 Meni je neshvatljivo

732
00:34:25,100 --> 00:34:27,180
 namja da mediji lažu.

733
00:34:27,180 --> 00:34:28,420
 ja ne mogu vjerovati

734
00:34:28,420 --> 00:34:29,880
 da tamo bude popis

735
00:34:29,880 --> 00:34:31,160
 nas Hrvata

736
00:34:31,160 --> 00:34:31,900
 u Hrvatskoj

737
00:34:31,900 --> 00:34:32,640
 i njih

738
00:34:32,640 --> 00:34:32,920
 onaj

739
00:34:32,920 --> 00:34:33,680
 osamdeset

740
00:34:33,680 --> 00:34:35,600
 i dva posto,

741
00:34:35,600 --> 00:34:36,500
 osamdeset četiri

742
00:34:36,500 --> 00:34:37,520
 onaj,

743
00:34:37,520 --> 00:34:39,120
 izjavi da su katolice.

744
00:34:39,120 --> 00:34:41,220
 Onda ih se pita,

745
00:34:41,220 --> 00:34:42,620
 ne znam,

746
00:34:42,620 --> 00:34:42,840
 nije

747
00:34:42,840 --> 00:34:44,880
 o kršćanskim načelima,

748
00:34:44,880 --> 00:34:45,820
 kažu

749
00:34:45,820 --> 00:34:47,020
 samo i dvajest i pet posto

750
00:34:47,020 --> 00:34:47,360
 za to.

751
00:34:47,600 --> 00:34:49,220
 a ne mogu vjerovati.

752
00:34:49,220 --> 00:34:53,000
 Šta se to događa?

753
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:53,660
 Viš kako smo mi

754
00:34:53,660 --> 00:34:54,720
 lutamo na obe strane.

755
00:34:54,720 --> 00:34:56,560
 Ne može tako,

756
00:34:56,560 --> 00:34:57,740
 moji lijepi prijatelji.

757
00:34:57,740 --> 00:34:59,880
 Kristu je dovoljno

758
00:34:59,880 --> 00:35:00,600
 dvoje ili troje.

759
00:35:00,600 --> 00:35:04,160
 Dvoje ili troje.

760
00:35:04,160 --> 00:35:07,580
 I s ovim završavam.

761
00:35:07,580 --> 00:35:09,560
 Cijelo jedno predavanje

762
00:35:09,560 --> 00:35:10,620
 se održao na naslo,

763
00:35:10,620 --> 00:35:11,000
 pa šta?

764
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:12,520
 Znate vi šta znači,

765
00:35:12,520 --> 00:35:12,860
 pa šta?

766
00:35:14,860 --> 00:35:16,420
 To je nevjerojatno.

767
00:35:16,420 --> 00:35:17,760
 Tu je kraj.

768
00:35:17,760 --> 00:35:19,300
 Znate, tu prestaje

769
00:35:19,300 --> 00:35:20,160
 razgovor

770
00:35:20,160 --> 00:35:21,180
 ili započinje

771
00:35:21,180 --> 00:35:23,420
 fundamentalno obraćanje,

772
00:35:23,420 --> 00:35:24,760
 promjena cijele svijesti,

773
00:35:24,760 --> 00:35:26,120
 pameti, srca, duše,

774
00:35:26,120 --> 00:35:27,680
 mozga i prsta

775
00:35:27,680 --> 00:35:28,420
 od male noge

776
00:35:28,420 --> 00:35:28,940
 i velike.

777
00:35:28,940 --> 00:35:32,000
 Znači kad ti ljudima kažeš

778
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:32,260
 onaj,

779
00:35:32,260 --> 00:35:34,720
 živite li s djevojkom,

780
00:35:34,720 --> 00:35:35,520
 a niste

781
00:35:35,520 --> 00:35:36,800
 kršćanski vjenčani?

782
00:35:36,800 --> 00:35:38,140
 Po šta?

783
00:35:38,140 --> 00:35:44,300
 Pa jesi li poštena

784
00:35:44,300 --> 00:35:44,740
 na poslu,

785
00:35:44,740 --> 00:35:45,300
 tamo si,

786
00:35:45,300 --> 00:35:47,160
 cementa je dovezeno

787
00:35:47,160 --> 00:35:48,040
 tri tone,

788
00:35:48,040 --> 00:35:48,960
 vi ste zapisali

789
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:49,720
 da je pet tona,

790
00:35:49,720 --> 00:35:50,820
 ove dvi tone su dolje

791
00:35:50,820 --> 00:35:51,620
 otišle na Jadran,

792
00:35:51,620 --> 00:35:52,940
 tvoji su vikendicu

793
00:35:52,940 --> 00:35:53,260
 onaj,

794
00:35:53,260 --> 00:35:54,300
 betonirale.

795
00:35:54,300 --> 00:35:55,120
 Pa šta?

796
00:35:55,120 --> 00:35:58,000
 I tako vam mogu brojiti

797
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:58,520
 do kraja.

798
00:35:58,520 --> 00:35:59,640
 To pa šta?

799
00:35:59,640 --> 00:36:00,300
 Znači,

800
00:36:00,300 --> 00:36:01,620
 drugi tako čine,

801
00:36:01,620 --> 00:36:02,500
 i ja tako čini,

802
00:36:02,500 --> 00:36:03,060
 nema Boga,

803
00:36:03,060 --> 00:36:03,760
 nema pravde,

804
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:04,600
 nema suda,

805
00:36:04,600 --> 00:36:05,160
 nema ničega.

806
00:36:05,160 --> 00:36:05,580
 Pa šta?

807
00:36:05,580 --> 00:36:09,500
 I druga?

808
00:36:09,500 --> 00:36:12,320
 Znate,

809
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:12,860
 ono dođu,

810
00:36:12,860 --> 00:36:13,240
 ne one,

811
00:36:13,240 --> 00:36:14,520
 dođu se ono dudon.

812
00:36:14,520 --> 00:36:16,440
 Što vi mislite,

813
00:36:16,440 --> 00:36:17,200
 ne znam,

814
00:36:17,200 --> 00:36:18,040
 ni o pobačaju?

815
00:36:18,040 --> 00:36:20,420
 Onda dođu,

816
00:36:20,420 --> 00:36:20,880
 ne znaš,

817
00:36:20,880 --> 00:36:21,680
 ono na pučle,

818
00:36:21,680 --> 00:36:22,600
 se usne ovdje,

819
00:36:22,600 --> 00:36:23,680
 tko voli,

820
00:36:23,680 --> 00:36:24,360
 neki izvoli.

821
00:36:28,260 --> 00:36:28,620
 Znate,

822
00:36:28,620 --> 00:36:29,340
 kako mi to,

823
00:36:29,340 --> 00:36:29,940
 jedno,

824
00:36:29,940 --> 00:36:30,760
 svi relativiziramo,

825
00:36:30,760 --> 00:36:31,760
 sad ja gledam neke ove,

826
00:36:31,760 --> 00:36:32,320
 koji su čak,

827
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:32,800
 oko na ime,

828
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:33,660
 naši katolici,

829
00:36:33,660 --> 00:36:35,080
 ovo kad se pita o pobačaj,

830
00:36:35,080 --> 00:36:35,720
 pa oni počnu,

831
00:36:35,720 --> 00:36:36,080
 znaš,

832
00:36:36,080 --> 00:36:37,020
 od Markova,

833
00:36:37,020 --> 00:36:37,600
 Konaka,

834
00:36:37,600 --> 00:36:38,240
 pa ovo,

835
00:36:38,240 --> 00:36:40,580
 nema o tome,

836
00:36:40,580 --> 00:36:42,160
 tu nema filozofije.

837
00:36:42,160 --> 00:36:44,140
 Jesi li zna,

838
00:36:44,140 --> 00:36:44,580
 daj ne?

839
00:36:44,580 --> 00:36:45,300
 Isu je rekao,

840
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:46,280
 vaš odgovornik bude da,

841
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:46,560
 da,

842
00:36:46,560 --> 00:36:47,300
 ili ne, ne.

843
00:36:47,300 --> 00:36:50,660
 Ne može kršćanska Isusova duša,

844
00:36:50,660 --> 00:36:51,840
 koja je gospodina susrla,

845
00:36:51,840 --> 00:36:52,760
 reći,

846
00:36:53,100 --> 00:36:54,640
 za stvari koje su grijeh,

847
00:36:54,640 --> 00:36:55,580
 tko voli,

848
00:36:55,580 --> 00:36:56,140
 neki izvoli.

849
00:36:56,140 --> 00:36:59,720
 E to nas ko šta,

850
00:36:59,720 --> 00:37:00,860
 to je ta laž,

851
00:37:00,860 --> 00:37:01,400
 paradoks,

852
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:02,600
 taj pa šta,

853
00:37:02,600 --> 00:37:03,900
 i tko voli,

854
00:37:03,900 --> 00:37:04,780
 neki izvoli.

855
00:37:04,780 --> 00:37:08,200
 Izvoli.

856
00:37:08,200 --> 00:37:11,240
 Hvala lijepo.

